<tr>
<th scope="row" class="navbox-group" style=";;">Teaching literacy</th>
<td style="text-align:left;border-left-width:2px;border-left-style:solid;width:100%;padding:0px;;;" class="navbox-list navbox-odd hlist">
<div style="padding:0em 0.25em">
<ul>
<li><a href="Reading_education_in_the_United_States" title="Reading education in the United States">Reading education in the USA</a></li>
